{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:13:21.483217+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's a summary of how to **start the admin app locally** and how to **build/preview for staging and production**, based on the repo's README, `package.json`, and environment files.\n\n---\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n1. **Clone** the repo and `cd` into it.\n2. Install **pnpm** globally (if not already):\n   ```bash\n   npm i -g pnpm\n   ```\n3. Install dependencies:\n   ```bash\n   pnpm install\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## Start Locally (Development)\n\n```bash\npnpm dev\n```\n\n- Runs `vue-cli-service serve` under the hood.\n- Uses the settings in **`.env.development`** (`ENV = 'development'`, `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/dev-api'`).\n- The app automatically opens at **http://localhost:9528**.\n\n---\n\n## Build for Staging\n\n```bash\npnpm build:stage\n```\n\n- Runs `vue-cli-service build --mode staging`.\n- Uses **`.env.staging`** (`NODE_ENV = production`, `ENV = 'staging'`, `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/stage-api'`).\n- Output goes to the default `dist/` directory.\n\n---\n\n## Build for Production\n\n```bash\npnpm build:prod\n```\n\n- Runs `vue-cli-service build` (default production mode).\n- Uses **`.env.production`** (`ENV = 'production'`, `VUE_APP_BASE_API = '/prod-api'`).\n- Output goes to `dist/`.\n\n---\n\n## Preview a Built Release\n\nAfter building (either staging or production), you can preview the result locally:\n\n```bash\npnpm preview               # preview the release build\npnpm preview -- --report    # preview + static resource analysis\n```\n\nThis runs `node build/index.js --preview`, which serves the contents of `dist/` so you can verify the build before deploying.\n\n---\n\n### Other Useful Commands\n\n| Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `pnpm lint` | Run ESLint code-format check |\n| `pnpm lint -- --fix` | Auto-fix lint issues |\n| `pnpm svgo` | Optimise SVG icons in `src/icons/svg/` |", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 499, "prompt_tokens": 10038, "total_tokens": 10537, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 27, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9600, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00065922, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.00022509, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00043413}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863191-nzzdqqbUyZeBa3JcXvjv", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3b7-cb01-7972-8d4c-561f3d186fd4-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10038, "output_tokens": 499, "total_tokens": 10537, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9600}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 27}}}}]}}}
